ite web|url =https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20191021004153-260402?chdtv|author =李文正|date =2019-10-21|title =前槍擊要犯藍信祺嗆殺蔡英文 遭逮送辦|publisher =[[中時電子報|中時電子報]]|access-date =2019-10-22|archive-date =2020-05-27|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200527021200/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20191021004153-260402?chdtv|dead-url =no}}</ref>。2019年11月2日連署期限結束後，中選會公布藍信祺未送出連署書，再度連署失敗<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191102/1570982.htm|title=呂秀蓮、法師、槍擊要犯連署總統都敗陣！800萬保證金進帳國庫|date=2019-11-02|website=ETtoday新聞雲|accessdate=2019-11-02|archive-date=2019-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102101147/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191102/1570982.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

